OL,3,C'Kindest, funniest' cyclist dies after
OL,4,Cswerving into van to avoid car
OL,6,FA cyclist has died after crashing into
OL,7,Fa stationary van while swerving to
OL,8,Favoid another car.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FRowson Street, in New Brighton, at
OL,12,Faround 11.30am on 5 June to reports
OL,13,Fthe cyclist had collided with a van
OL,14,Fwaiting at traffic lights as he
OL,15,Fswerved to avoid a Nissan Micra.
OL,17,FJohn Edward Carr, 68, was taken to
OL,18,Fhospital in a critical condition but
OL,19,Flater died from his injuries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
