OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780851961
OL,3,C'Kindest, funniest' cyclist dies after
OL,4,Cswerving into van to avoid car
OL,6,FA 65-year-old woman from Wallasey was
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of causing death
OL,8,Fby careless driving and failing to
OL,9,Fstop at the scene of a collision.
OL,11,FShe was taken to a police station for
OL,12,Fquestioning and has since been
OL,13,Freleased under investigation.
OL,15,FThe van driver stopped at the scene
OL,16,Fand is assisting officers with their
OL,17,Fenquiries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
