CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780851961
OL,3,C'Kindest, funniest' cyclist dies after
OL,4,Cswerving into van to avoid car
OL,6,FPaying tribute to John, his family
OL,7,Fdescribed him as "one of the kindest,
OL,8,Ffunniest, most open minded people you
OL,9,Fcould meet".
OL,11,F"He had such a big heart and he never
OL,12,Freally lost that childlike sense of
OL,13,Fwonder," they said in a tribute.
OL,15,F"He could find joy in the simplest
OL,16,Fthings, including staying up far too
OL,17,Flate playing golf games on his VR
OL,18,Fheadset, or chuckling away at silly
OL,19,FYouTube videos.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
