FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780851961
OL,3,C'Kindest, funniest' cyclist dies after
OL,4,Cswerving into van to avoid car
OL,6,F"He spent 27 years working as a cook
OL,7,Fin the Merchant Navy and had so many
OL,8,Fwild and hilarious stories from his
OL,9,Flife. He would never fail to make us
OL,10,Flaugh or look out for us and he always
OL,11,Floved us unconditionally.
OL,13,F"We still can't understand how he has
OL,14,Fbeen taken from us so suddenly. It
OL,15,Fdoesn't feel real.
OL,17,F"We don't want him to just become
OL,18,Fanother headline. He was a real
OL,19,Fperson. He was loved and he mattered".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
