PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780851961
OL,3,C'Kindest, funniest' cyclist dies after
OL,4,Cswerving into van to avoid car
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Kurt Timpson, the
OL,7,FLead Investigating Officer from
OL,8,FMerseyside Police's Serious Collision
OL,9,FInvestigation Unit, said: "First and
OL,10,Fforemost, my thoughts and those of my
OL,11,Fteam are with the man's family at this
OL,12,Fdesperately sad time. For someone to
OL,13,Flose their life on the road is tragic
OL,14,Fand my priority now is to get answers
OL,15,Ffor his family.
OL,17,F"Although a woman was later traced and
OL,18,Farrested, we are still keen to gather
OL,19,Fas much dashcam and other footage as
OL,20,Fpossible.
OL,26,@qD@[OUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780851961
OL,3,C'Kindest, funniest' cyclist dies after
OL,4,Cswerving into van to avoid car
OL,6,F"Please check any devices and come
OL,7,Fforward if you live, work or were
OL,8,Fpassing the area around the time of
OL,9,Fthe collision. Front and rear dashcams
OL,10,Fcan often capture vital evidence
OL,11,Fwithout the driver being aware. Please
OL,12,Freview those devices and if you can
OL,13,Fhelp, get in touch with our team.
OL,15,F"Any help we receive, no matter how
OL,16,Finsignificant it may seem, could be
OL,17,Fvital as we build a picture of what
OL,18,Fhappened.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
