CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1780851961
OL,3,C'Kindest, funniest' cyclist dies after
OL,4,Cswerving into van to avoid car
OL,6,F"I also want to thank the members of
OL,7,Fthe public who rushed to help the man
OL,8,Fas he lay injured. It's often the case
OL,9,Fthat we see the very best of human
OL,10,Fnature after such distressing events."
OL,12,FAnyone with information should contact
OL,13,FMerseyside Police social media desk
OL,14,Fvia X or Facebook with reference
OL,15,F26000446913.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
